h extensive simulations, efficiency of the proposed RSMD\nalgorithm over several benchmark schemes is demonstrated\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jul 2020 23:55:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 05:51:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 5 Feb 2021 20:36:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 15 Apr 2021 03:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-16"}
