o the galaxy power spectrum may\nallow for further improvements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jul 2020 10:24:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2021 20:46:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-18"}
