R Models}, \\emph{Attacks\\&Defenses}, and\n\\emph{Evaluations} at\n\\url{https://github.com/ShawnXYang/Face-Robustness-Benchmark}, which will be\ncontinuously updated to promote future research on robust FR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jul 2020 13:39:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 08:01:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-30"}
